  "metadata": {
    "title": "Pomodoro Timer — Multi‑method Focus Session Calculator",
    "description": "Configurable Pomodoro timer calculator with multiple officially documented methods (standard, long-focus, ultradian, and custom). Estimates total focused minutes, elapsed time including breaks, and focus share. Includes calibration, limits, and references to relevant standards for timekeeping, ergonomics, and workplace breaks."
